1065cc'),(630,142,'detailed','Day 1: Getting Your Hands Dirty  Introduction to Pottery\r\nYour journey into the world of ceramics begins with an immersive introduction to the history and cultural significance of Vietnamese pottery.\r\n\r\n Meet your expert artisan instructors, who will share stories of their familys multi-generational pottery legacy.\r\n Get familiar with different types of clay and learn how to prepare it for shaping.\r\n Hands-on session: Learn the basic techniques of shaping clay using a traditional spinning wheel.\r\n Experiment with different forms: cups, bowls, vases, or whatever your imagination creates!\r\n\r\nAt the end of the first day, your pieces will be set aside for drying and first-stage firing in a traditional kiln.\r\n\r\nDay 2: Finishing Touches  Glazing & Decorating Your Masterpiece\r\nOn the second day, its time to bring color and personality to your pottery!\r\n\r\n Learn the art of glazing and decorating ceramics, using traditional Vietnamese patterns and motifs.\r\n Watch as your pieces go through the final firing process, turning soft clay into durable pottery.\r\n Once cooled, you can take home your unique ceramic creation  a perfect souvenir of your cultural journey in Vietnam!\r\n\r\nWhether youre looking for a fun, hands-on experience or a deeper appreciation of Vietnamese artistry, this workshop offers both.\r\n\r\n Book now and create a masterpiece with your own hands!\r\n\r\n Why Join This Workshop?\r\n Authentic Experience  Learn directly from skilled artisans.\r\n Hands-On Fun  Shape, design, and glaze your own pottery.\r\n Take Home Your Creation  A truly unique souvenir.\r\n Perfect for All Skill Levels  No prior experience needed!\r\n\r\nReady to get your hands messy and create something special? Book your spot today! '),(631,142,'_detailed','field_67c2f9ea065cd'),(632,142,'gallery','149'),(633,142,'_gallery','field_67c307d31c35d'),(634,150,'description','Master the ancient craft of Vietnamese pottery and create y