s to make it uniquely yours!\r\n\r\n Step 3: Lighting Up & Taking Home Your Masterpiece\r\nAs your lantern takes shape, youll learn how to insert a light source and adjust it for the perfect glow.\r\n\r\n Once finished, youll receive a protective box to carry your handmade lantern home safely!\r\n\r\nWhether you\'re looking to decorate your home, gift a loved one, or simply enjoy a cultural experience, this workshop will leave you with beautiful memories and a stunning handmade lantern!\r\n\r\nWhy You Should Join This Workshop\r\n Authentic Experience  Learn from expert Vietnamese artisans.\r\n Fun & Interactive  A creative hands-on activity for all ages.\r\n Take Home a Unique Souvenir  A handcrafted lantern made by YOU.\r\n Perfect for Families & Couples  A beautiful bonding experience.\r\n\r\n Book your spot today and illuminate your journey in Hi An! '),(680,151,'_detailed','field_67c2f9ea065cd'),(681,151,'gallery','152'),(682,151,'_gallery','field_67c307d31c35d'),(683,153,'description','Craft a traditional Vietnamese lantern to capture the essence of Hi An.'),(684,153,'_description','field_67bc303439347'),(685,153,'date','20250319'),(686,153,'_date','field_67c307a41c35c'),(687,153,'location','Hoi An'),(688,153,'_location','field_67bc308e1f7ce'),(689,153,'discount','20% OFF'),(690,153,'_discount','field_67bc30731f7cd'),(691,153,'duration','1 day'),(692,153,'_duration','field_67bc30951f7cf'),(693,153,'thumbnail','144'),(694,153,'_thumbnail','field_67bc309b1f7d0'),(695,153,'overview','Step into the magical world of Hi An\'s traditional lantern-making and experience an art form that has been passed down for generations. Known as the City of Lanterns, Hi Ans vibrant streets are lit up by beautifully handcrafted lanterns, symbolizing prosperity, happiness, and good fortune.\r\n\r\nIn this hands-on Lantern Making Workshop, you will:\r\n Learn the history and cultural significance of Hi Ans lanterns.\r\n Choose from a variety of colors, shapes, and patterns.\r\n Get gu